# APT1040_WEBSITE
A hair and beauty website for business. It features a sleek design, easy navigation to branches, partners, and product inventory, and includes an integrated YouTube video and product showcase with prices. Customers can easily browse and place orders online.
Features:
Homepage with a Welcoming interface with company logo and a marquee message.
Navigation Menu: Easy access to key sections:
Branches: View different store locations.
Partners: Links to our partners like Jumia.
Contact Us: Get in touch via email.
Signup: Register for exclusive offers and services.
Inventory: Explore our extensive product collection.
Order: Convenient order form for purchasing.
Meet the Team: Learn about the people behind PRIME WIGS.
Product Showcase: Display of products with images, descriptions, prices, and add-to-cart functionality.
YouTube Integration: Embedded video to showcase product usage and customer testimonials.
Responsive Design: Clean and user-friendly layout with a vibrant green background.
